---
import DocLayout from '../../../../layouts/DocLayout.astro';
import { Alert } from '@docs/ui/components';

const lang = 'en';
const version = 'v2';
---

<DocLayout title="Getting Started" lang={lang} version={version}>
  <p>Welcome to our documentation! This guide will help you get started with our platform.</p>
  
  <Alert type="info">
    This is the documentation for version 2.0. If you're using version 1.0, please <a href="/en/v1/guide/getting-started">click here</a>.
  </Alert>
  
  <h2>Prerequisites</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Node.js 18 or higher</li>
    <li>npm, yarn, or pnpm</li>
    <li>Basic knowledge of JavaScript</li>
  </ul>
  
  <h2>Installation</h2>
  <p>You can install our package using npm:</p>
  
  <pre><code>npm install @our-package/core@2.0.0</code></pre>
  
  <p>Or using yarn:</p>
  
  <pre><code>yarn add @our-package/core@2.0.0</code></pre>
  
  <p>Or using pnpm:</p>
  
  <pre><code>pnpm add @our-package/core@2.0.0</code></pre>
  
  <h2>Basic Usage</h2>
  <p>Here's a simple example of how to use our package:</p>
  
  <pre><code>import { createApp } from '@our-package/core';

// New in v2: Async/await support
async function initializeApp() {
  const app = await createApp({
    // Configuration options
    debug: true,
    mode: 'development',
    // New in v2: Enhanced options
    plugins: ['logger', 'analytics'],
    performance: {
      monitoring: true,
      metrics: ['cpu', 'memory']
    }
  });

  await app.start();
}

initializeApp();</code></pre>
  
  <h2>New Features in v2</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Full async/await support</li>
    <li>Enhanced plugin system</li>
    <li>Performance monitoring</li>
    <li>Improved error handling</li>
    <li>TypeScript type definitions included</li>
  </ul>
  
  <h2>Next Steps</h2>
  <p>Now that you have the basics set up, you can:</p>
  
  <ul>
    <li>Learn more about <a href={`/${lang}/${version}/guide/configuration`}>configuration options</a></li>
    <li>Explore the <a href={`/${lang}/${version}/api/reference`}>API reference</a></li>
    <li>Check out some <a href={`/${lang}/${version}/examples`}>examples</a></li>
    <li>Read about <a href={`/${lang}/${version}/guide/migration`}>migrating from v1</a></li>
  </ul>
</DocLayout>
